WEBVTT

01:25.800 --> 01:34.950
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.340 --> 01:37.930
[Episode 9]

01:38.400 --> 01:39.270
Ranran,

01:39.450 --> 01:41.920
becoming a great superstar is

01:42.680 --> 01:44.140
just around the corner!

01:44.200 --> 01:45.120
-Nice!
-Nice!

01:45.140 --> 01:45.740
Well said!

01:46.070 --> 01:46.729
Bravo.

01:47.120 --> 01:48.370
I'll drink this third glass for her.

01:48.370 --> 01:49.370
-No, no!
-Come on.

01:50.450 --> 01:52.039
This is my celebratory dinner.

01:52.039 --> 01:53.300
Can't break the rules.

01:53.400 --> 01:53.870
That's right!

01:53.870 --> 01:54.200
OK.

01:55.090 --> 01:55.550
Come on.

01:55.600 --> 01:56.039
Let's drink with her.

01:56.039 --> 01:57.370
-Cheers! Come on!
-Cheers!

01:57.370 --> 01:58.300
Cheers! Cheers!

01:59.090 --> 01:59.950
-Congrats!
-Congrats!

01:59.950 --> 02:00.780
Congrats!

02:00.840 --> 02:01.440
Thank you!

02:05.480 --> 02:07.060
Look how lively it is!

02:07.150 --> 02:08.550
I heard you from outside!

02:09.360 --> 02:11.060
You haven't touched the food.
Waiting for me?

02:11.060 --> 02:11.800
Sit, sit.

02:12.180 --> 02:13.680
Grab a chair. There's one over there.

02:13.680 --> 02:15.430
You know what, I didn't come for nothing.

02:15.430 --> 02:16.500
Here's another dish for you.

02:16.500 --> 02:17.020
Come on.

02:17.810 --> 02:18.810
This is great.

02:18.810 --> 02:19.540
Refreshing.

02:21.360 --> 02:21.930
Just a little.

02:21.930 --> 02:22.790
Zhuang Zhuang,

02:22.930 --> 02:24.130
here's a toast to you.

02:25.030 --> 02:25.900
Thanks for styling

02:25.900 --> 02:27.300
so many beautiful outfits for me.

02:27.300 --> 02:28.000
It was nothing.

02:28.000 --> 02:29.210
-I'll chug it. You don't have to.
-Pace yourself.

02:29.210 --> 02:30.410
Don't drink too much.

02:30.460 --> 02:31.590
Count me in. Come on.

02:32.210 --> 02:34.390
Ranran is an honest drinker.

02:35.079 --> 02:37.010
Drinking manners show character.

02:37.310 --> 02:38.510
Downing every glass.

02:38.590 --> 02:39.930
I feel so great today.

02:40.710 --> 02:41.500
Well,

02:41.620 --> 02:42.579
since I came to Beijing...

02:42.579 --> 02:43.500
Can you drink less?

02:43.500 --> 02:45.780
-I've been holding this grudge in my heart.
-I'm fine.

02:45.780 --> 02:47.310
Now I've finally let it out.

02:47.740 --> 02:48.190
No.

02:49.240 --> 02:50.240
I can't hold it in.

02:50.590 --> 02:51.520
Need to throw up?

02:51.780 --> 02:52.710
No, Zhuang.

02:53.860 --> 02:55.590
I mean, I can't hold my words in.

02:56.370 --> 02:56.810
Then say it.

02:56.810 --> 02:57.150
Ranran,

02:57.150 --> 02:58.990
say whatever you want.

02:59.130 --> 02:59.840
Just don't throw up.

02:59.840 --> 03:01.180
-In front of such a feast...
-No! Throw up!

03:01.180 --> 03:01.980
Throw up all you want!

03:01.980 --> 03:03.080
I'm sitting right here.

03:03.080 --> 03:03.750
Throw up all you want.

03:03.750 --> 03:04.500
You're gross.

03:04.500 --> 03:05.370
Will you catch it with your mouth?

03:05.370 --> 03:06.170
I'll catch it!

03:07.910 --> 03:08.780
What's going on?

03:08.780 --> 03:09.150
No.

03:09.370 --> 03:10.170
-Give it to me.
-Shen.

03:10.170 --> 03:10.970
The microphone!

03:10.970 --> 03:11.650
The microphone.

03:11.650 --> 03:12.580
The microphone.

03:12.750 --> 03:13.150
Mic...

03:14.030 --> 03:14.570
She's...

03:14.800 --> 03:15.620
She's on stage!

03:15.620 --> 03:17.060
Come on, let's give her a big hand!

03:17.060 --> 03:18.060
Come on, applaud!

03:19.300 --> 03:20.300
Quiet, everyone.

03:22.020 --> 03:25.690
I came from Huzhou to Beijing,

03:27.180 --> 03:30.520
and moved into this Seasons Change Hostel.

03:31.590 --> 03:32.720
After all this time,

03:33.079 --> 03:35.930
I've never been this happy before.

03:36.590 --> 03:37.990
Never been this excited.

03:38.140 --> 03:39.100
Hear, hear.

03:39.130 --> 03:40.130
My friends,

03:40.870 --> 03:41.860
do you know what?

03:43.280 --> 03:44.010
I've made it!

03:44.180 --> 03:45.579
I've succeeded!

03:47.150 --> 03:48.590
I didn't understand a word you said.

03:48.590 --> 03:49.130
She said she's succeeded.

03:49.130 --> 03:50.650
Actors must speak in Standard Mandarin.

03:50.650 --> 03:51.670
I've made it!

03:51.970 --> 03:52.960
Did you hear me?

03:53.000 --> 03:54.890
We heard you!

03:55.079 --> 03:56.340
We heard you this time.

03:56.860 --> 03:57.340
Why...

03:58.210 --> 03:59.600
did I succeed?

04:00.460 --> 04:02.460
Because I always held on to the faith

04:02.530 --> 04:04.000
that I am a good actress.

04:05.500 --> 04:06.190
At 7,

04:06.250 --> 04:08.110
in the Children's Palace Dance Competition,

04:08.110 --> 04:09.240
I was the runner-up.

04:09.800 --> 04:10.950
My backflip kick

04:11.090 --> 04:12.810
made the judges' jaws drop.

04:13.430 --> 04:14.890
I sang, acted, and fought.

04:15.780 --> 04:18.040
The applause was thunderous.

04:18.300 --> 04:19.370
Thunderous!

04:19.390 --> 04:22.510
Thunderous, just thunderous!

04:23.180 --> 04:23.980
At 10,

04:24.190 --> 04:25.500
I'd already made an appearance

04:25.500 --> 04:26.330
in movies.

04:26.830 --> 04:27.650
At 12,

04:28.130 --> 04:29.750
I was already a child star.

04:30.060 --> 04:31.150
And at 17,

04:31.250 --> 04:32.409
a director

04:32.980 --> 04:33.640
cast me

04:33.690 --> 04:34.630
to play

04:34.630 --> 04:35.710
a major role.

04:36.560 --> 04:37.250
But I was

04:38.480 --> 04:40.800
replaced by someone with connections.

04:43.159 --> 04:44.510
Knowing the danger,

04:45.680 --> 04:47.190
I marched right into the tiger's den!

04:47.190 --> 04:49.090
My artist dream

04:49.240 --> 04:51.440
flew and flew,

04:51.830 --> 04:53.500
like a young eagle,

04:53.980 --> 04:55.240
all the way to Beijing.

04:55.450 --> 04:56.980
Dived right into this city!

04:57.250 --> 04:59.480
Unafraid of the storms and rolling waves.

04:59.480 --> 05:00.870
I am a good actress.

05:01.500 --> 05:02.360
I believe in it,

05:02.770 --> 05:04.570
and you should believe in it too.

05:04.950 --> 05:06.970
My artist dream

05:07.220 --> 05:08.900
will bloom brilliantly,

05:09.130 --> 05:10.480
flourishing in full glory!

05:10.480 --> 05:11.480
-Nice!
-Bravo!

05:11.510 --> 05:12.330
Nice!

05:12.810 --> 05:13.210
Bravo!

05:13.240 --> 05:14.030
Well said!

05:14.130 --> 05:16.590
I've yearned for Beijing
since I was little,

05:16.930 --> 05:17.980
singing every day:

05:17.980 --> 05:20.490
"I love Beijing Tiananmen.

05:20.810 --> 05:22.300
The sun rises above Tianan..."

05:22.300 --> 05:25.200
"I love Beijing Tiananmen.

05:25.240 --> 05:29.430
The sun rises above Tiananmen.

05:29.500 --> 05:31.750
The great leader Chairman Mao

05:31.930 --> 05:35.920
leads all of us forward."

05:51.680 --> 05:52.480
Morning, sir.

05:52.480 --> 05:53.010
Morning.

05:55.450 --> 05:56.250
Morning, sir.

06:11.560 --> 06:12.300
Production Assistant?

06:12.300 --> 06:13.680
Here! I'm here!

06:15.560 --> 06:16.660
Your job today

06:16.800 --> 06:18.270
is to clean up this car.

06:18.750 --> 06:19.280
This car?

06:19.510 --> 06:21.250
Yes. We need it soon.

06:21.300 --> 06:21.990
OK, sure!

06:22.120 --> 06:23.980
Here are the keys to the prop room.

06:25.620 --> 06:26.570
I'm going to test drive it.

06:26.570 --> 06:27.450
Drive safe!

06:27.500 --> 06:28.070
Sure!

06:31.000 --> 06:31.630
Look at this dust.

06:31.630 --> 06:32.980
Look at all this dust in here.

06:32.980 --> 06:33.430
You...

06:34.120 --> 06:34.870
Hey, Lin.

06:34.870 --> 06:35.740
I don't mean to lecture you.

06:35.740 --> 06:36.420
Every day, you come to me

06:36.420 --> 06:37.620
asking for manpower and money,

06:37.620 --> 06:38.159
but your props

06:38.159 --> 06:39.140
are this shoddy?

06:39.270 --> 06:39.950
No, Manager.

06:39.950 --> 06:40.659
Don't be mad.

06:40.659 --> 06:41.250
Look.

06:41.390 --> 06:42.690
It'll surely look better tomorrow.

06:42.690 --> 06:43.300
If it doesn't,

06:43.300 --> 06:44.560
I'll get someone else to do this.

06:44.560 --> 06:46.159
No, please, don't, Manager!

06:46.250 --> 06:46.930
Come here.

06:46.950 --> 06:47.850
Come on.

06:48.630 --> 06:49.450
Wait a second.

06:56.600 --> 06:57.330
My cousin just

06:57.330 --> 06:58.370
came from our hometown.

06:58.370 --> 07:00.570
He brought you some local specialties.

07:00.920 --> 07:01.430
Not here.

07:01.430 --> 07:02.760
Send it to my room later.

07:05.100 --> 07:05.630
Manager.

07:05.920 --> 07:07.330
Is that new production assistant

07:07.330 --> 07:08.330
a relative of the director?

07:08.330 --> 07:09.370
What relative?

07:09.370 --> 07:11.630
I heard he's just an amateur enthusiast.

07:11.740 --> 07:12.810
The director pitied him,

07:12.810 --> 07:14.360
so he let him join the crew
to give him a shot.

07:14.360 --> 07:15.830
This kid hasn't done anything before.

07:15.830 --> 07:17.130
He's bound to screw up sooner or later.

07:17.130 --> 07:17.980
I'll tell you what.

07:17.980 --> 07:18.860
Once he makes a mistake,

07:18.860 --> 07:20.040
I'll mention it to the director

07:20.040 --> 07:20.720
that he isn't

07:20.720 --> 07:21.650
cut out for this.

07:22.010 --> 07:23.610
And that will be the end of it.

07:24.000 --> 07:25.060
I'm just worried

07:25.060 --> 07:26.100
that with him

07:26.240 --> 07:27.240
taking the spot,

07:27.240 --> 07:29.300
what I asked you for will be hopeless.

07:29.330 --> 07:30.060
No way.

07:32.190 --> 07:32.720
Manager.

07:33.220 --> 07:33.720
Lin.

07:41.810 --> 07:43.010
Not cut out for it?

07:44.420 --> 07:47.130
I've never seen anyone
more cut out for it than me.

07:47.130 --> 07:49.900
[East Shore Club]

08:18.010 --> 08:19.470
Hello. Are you Ms. Zhang?

08:21.930 --> 08:22.790
Uh... No, I'm not.

08:22.790 --> 08:23.740
Then you can't sit here.

08:23.740 --> 08:25.150
This table is reserved.

08:27.630 --> 08:28.980
I... I'm waiting for someone.

08:28.980 --> 08:30.100
I'll leave right away.

08:30.100 --> 08:31.200
You can sit for a while.

08:31.200 --> 08:32.390
But you have to order something.

08:32.390 --> 08:33.520
What would you like?

08:36.630 --> 08:37.150
I...

08:38.490 --> 08:39.900
I-I'll have a soda.

08:40.169 --> 08:41.030
The rule is that

08:41.549 --> 08:42.940
you can only order alcohol.

08:42.940 --> 08:43.289
But

08:43.620 --> 08:45.170
aren't they drinking soda?

08:45.630 --> 08:46.750
They are regulars.

08:46.840 --> 08:47.970
How is that the same?

08:48.220 --> 08:49.150
What'd you like?

08:50.130 --> 08:51.410
Why are you discriminating against me?

08:51.410 --> 08:52.760
What discrimination?

08:53.080 --> 08:53.910
Hey, this is a bar!

08:53.910 --> 08:55.170
What'd you order if not alcohol?

08:55.170 --> 08:55.790
Order you?

08:55.940 --> 08:57.430
How could you say that?

08:57.460 --> 08:58.270
What'd I say wrong?

08:58.270 --> 08:59.630
Everyone, come and take a look.

08:59.630 --> 09:01.030
This woman is a freeloader.

09:01.030 --> 09:02.640
She wouldn't order anything.

09:02.640 --> 09:04.360
I just said I'm ordering a soda!

09:04.360 --> 09:05.240
Did you hear me?

09:05.260 --> 09:06.250
Apologize to me!

09:06.290 --> 09:07.010
Stop insulting me,

09:07.010 --> 09:07.370
OK?

09:07.370 --> 09:08.270
I'm done talking to you.

09:08.270 --> 09:09.220
Please leave now.

09:09.220 --> 09:10.170
You're not welcome here.

09:10.170 --> 09:10.960
Don't touch me!

09:10.960 --> 09:12.490
Move! Come outside with me!

09:12.620 --> 09:14.050
-Why should I apologize?
-Cut it out.

09:14.050 --> 09:14.840
Why are you dragging me?

09:14.840 --> 09:16.170
Make him apologize to me!

09:16.170 --> 09:16.940
She's my friend.

09:16.940 --> 09:17.620
Apologize to me!

09:17.620 --> 09:18.120
Ranran. Ranran.

09:18.120 --> 09:18.910
I'll apologize to you.

09:18.910 --> 09:19.840
I'll apologize.

09:20.100 --> 09:20.580
Ranran!

09:21.410 --> 09:21.980
You hit my tooth.

09:21.980 --> 09:22.930
Let go of me!

09:23.000 --> 09:24.010
I'll apologize to you.

09:24.010 --> 09:26.050
You don't know the situation at all!

09:26.140 --> 09:27.460
It was clearly their fault!

09:27.460 --> 09:28.730
It is their fault!

09:29.010 --> 09:30.410
Isn't my apology enough?

09:31.030 --> 09:32.960
Do you know what they said about me?

09:33.220 --> 09:35.020
They said I was soliciting here.

09:35.840 --> 09:37.370
It's obviously a rip-off joint.

09:37.370 --> 09:37.890
I'm going to find...

09:37.890 --> 09:38.600
No, don't!

09:39.460 --> 09:40.100
You have no idea

09:40.100 --> 09:41.840
how many guests have complained about him.

09:41.840 --> 09:42.550
He won't last long.

09:42.550 --> 09:43.440
They'll get rid of him soon.

09:43.440 --> 09:44.770
He's hurting business.

09:44.870 --> 09:46.500
He is the boss's relative.

09:46.740 --> 09:48.290
If you go complain about him now,

09:48.290 --> 09:49.890
I'll lose my job too, won't I?

09:50.620 --> 09:51.630
On behalf of my boss,

09:51.630 --> 09:52.220
the bar,

09:52.480 --> 09:53.750
and on his behalf, I'll apologize to you.

09:53.750 --> 09:54.350
I'm sorry.

09:54.370 --> 09:55.290
I apologize, OK?

09:55.290 --> 09:56.370
It's my fault. I'm sorry.

09:56.370 --> 09:57.700
You always take other people's sides.

09:57.700 --> 09:58.980
I didn't...

09:59.100 --> 10:00.020
Get out of my way.

10:00.020 --> 10:00.700
Move.

10:06.910 --> 10:08.480
Watch where you're going.

10:30.010 --> 10:31.210
Why did you come here?

10:32.060 --> 10:33.030
To see me?

10:34.440 --> 10:35.170
I forgot to ask you.

10:35.170 --> 10:36.970
How was my performance just now?

10:40.010 --> 10:40.960
It was OK.

10:41.220 --> 10:42.070
Come anytime.

10:42.410 --> 10:43.340
Mention my name.

10:44.100 --> 10:46.230
Listen all you want, and sit anywhere.

10:46.460 --> 10:47.720
You're just bragging.

10:48.200 --> 10:50.000
I'm never coming back
to this rip-off joint.

10:50.000 --> 10:51.700
Then where do you want to listen?

10:51.700 --> 10:53.320
I'll play for you there.

10:55.870 --> 10:56.340
I want to go

10:56.340 --> 10:57.870
to the lotus pond to listen.

10:58.370 --> 11:00.970
Then I'll sit on a lotus
and play the sax for you.

11:02.390 --> 11:02.840
Wouldn't I...

11:02.840 --> 11:04.500
Wouldn't I become Nezha then?

11:06.100 --> 11:07.170
You have the Wind and Fire Wheels?

11:07.170 --> 11:08.460
I do have the Wind and Fire Wheels.

11:08.460 --> 11:09.630
You've ridden them.

11:09.670 --> 11:10.650
Either on the crossbar,

11:10.650 --> 11:11.500
or on the back seat.

11:11.500 --> 11:13.550
-I'll kick the wheels...
-Enough fibbing.

11:13.550 --> 11:14.500
Hurry back.

11:14.510 --> 11:15.390
The customers are waiting for you.

11:15.390 --> 11:16.450
I'm not going back.

11:16.890 --> 11:18.630
With you upset and angry,

11:18.630 --> 11:19.760
why should I go back?

11:19.770 --> 11:20.700
I quit. I'm done.

11:21.940 --> 11:22.940
Quit?

11:23.580 --> 11:24.670
It's so hard to find a job nowadays.

11:24.670 --> 11:25.870
Go back immediately!

11:28.270 --> 11:29.750
My performance is over.

11:29.860 --> 11:31.660
It's someone else's turn now.

11:34.530 --> 11:35.750
You're so annoying!

11:37.410 --> 11:38.740
I... I'll walk you back.

11:41.200 --> 11:42.000
Let's go then.

11:42.820 --> 11:43.580
Perfect timing.

11:43.580 --> 11:44.640
You should take a break too.

11:44.640 --> 11:46.640
You've been playing the sax all day.

11:47.900 --> 11:49.360
Let's go find the lotuses.

11:50.000 --> 11:51.000
Hurry up and come.

11:51.630 --> 11:52.770
I know where there are lotuses

11:52.770 --> 11:53.630
ready to bloom!

11:59.050 --> 11:59.860
Just now,

12:00.600 --> 12:01.360
didn't we say

12:01.910 --> 12:02.460
we were

12:03.080 --> 12:04.280
looking for lotuses?

12:05.120 --> 12:08.240
There... There are no lotuses around here.

12:11.410 --> 12:11.980
Nezha.

12:12.720 --> 12:13.740
Nezha? I'm Nezha?

12:15.620 --> 12:16.420
Are you tired?

12:17.100 --> 12:17.630
How about

12:18.480 --> 12:19.880
we sit here and rest a bit?

12:21.030 --> 12:21.620
Sure.

12:28.030 --> 12:28.490
Ranran.

12:29.170 --> 12:30.710
Wait for me a second.

12:30.940 --> 12:31.960
W-Where are you going?

12:31.960 --> 12:32.790
Just wait a second.

12:32.790 --> 12:33.850
I'll be right back.

12:47.340 --> 12:47.800
Ranran.

12:48.730 --> 12:49.580
Didn't you say

12:49.580 --> 12:50.980
you wanted a soda?

12:51.670 --> 12:53.240
I found a grocery store over there.

12:53.240 --> 12:54.640
They happened to sell it.

12:54.670 --> 12:55.870
Let's drink and chat.

12:59.790 --> 13:00.870
Thank you.

13:05.750 --> 13:06.590
It's so sweet.

13:07.700 --> 13:10.030
Let's drink for a while before going back.

13:10.770 --> 13:11.600
Don't they say a chat

13:11.600 --> 13:13.730
lasts for the time of an incense stick?

13:13.890 --> 13:14.550
The two of us

13:16.070 --> 13:17.730
can chat for the time of a coil.

13:18.740 --> 13:20.740
Where did you get the mosquito coil?

13:21.240 --> 13:22.960
When I bought the soda,

13:23.000 --> 13:24.620
I thought there must be many

13:24.620 --> 13:25.950
mosquitoes by the lake.

13:26.150 --> 13:27.280
I figured

13:28.500 --> 13:30.260
I couldn't let you get bitten.

13:31.050 --> 13:32.890
Our chat shouldn't end with us

13:33.290 --> 13:35.220
covered in mosquito bites, right?

13:35.770 --> 13:37.170
This coil of incense will

13:37.770 --> 13:38.970
give us some time too.

13:44.620 --> 13:46.000
What do you think of me?

13:49.530 --> 13:50.460
You're alright.

13:54.480 --> 13:55.410
That's it?

13:56.320 --> 13:58.320
We have a whole coil's worth of time.

13:58.750 --> 13:59.950
Elaborate a bit more.

14:03.550 --> 14:06.010
At first, when we were at the small hostel,

14:06.010 --> 14:07.410
I thought you were just

14:07.820 --> 14:08.910
a smooth talker

14:08.910 --> 14:10.240
and didn't seem decent.

14:12.410 --> 14:13.740
But I felt that you were definitely

14:13.740 --> 14:14.840
not a bad person.

14:16.120 --> 14:18.240
What surprised me most was that

14:18.910 --> 14:19.890
you, a Beijing local,

14:19.890 --> 14:21.550
actually lived in a basement.

14:23.600 --> 14:25.670
It's a long story.

14:26.650 --> 14:27.580
Tell me about it.

14:30.360 --> 14:32.670
I'll keep it short.

14:33.790 --> 14:35.460
Well, my dad and I

14:36.630 --> 14:37.890
had a little conflict.

14:38.170 --> 14:38.720
Basically,

14:38.720 --> 14:39.770
what he wants me to do

14:39.770 --> 14:40.830
and what I want to do

14:40.980 --> 14:42.590
are never on the same page.

14:43.100 --> 14:43.720
And then,

14:43.720 --> 14:45.700
he kept finding ways to lecture me.

14:45.720 --> 14:46.890
I got annoyed by all the talk.

14:46.890 --> 14:48.450
But I know him.

14:49.030 --> 14:49.360
He

14:50.240 --> 14:51.840
certainly wouldn't harm me.

14:52.320 --> 14:53.150
One thing led to another,

14:53.150 --> 14:54.750
and I didn't want to live at home anymore.

14:54.750 --> 14:55.940
So I moved out.

14:56.650 --> 14:58.270
That's about it.

15:00.550 --> 15:01.130
I see.

15:02.890 --> 15:04.290
That's not complicated.

15:05.290 --> 15:06.530
Don't you want to persuade me?

15:06.530 --> 15:07.990
Why should I persuade you?

15:08.150 --> 15:09.080
You're well aware

15:09.080 --> 15:10.210
that they mean well.

15:10.720 --> 15:12.490
Besides, the world is so big.

15:12.630 --> 15:13.770
Not everyone's opinions

15:13.770 --> 15:15.030
can be on the same page.

15:15.910 --> 15:16.930
And

15:17.530 --> 15:18.990
as long as no one gets hurt,

15:19.340 --> 15:21.600
understanding is the highest standard.

15:25.480 --> 15:26.910
Out of everyone I've ever met,

15:26.910 --> 15:28.110
not including my mom,

15:29.080 --> 15:32.530
you're the woman of the highest standard.

15:34.620 --> 15:36.310
What are you talking about?

15:37.460 --> 15:38.460
When I first

15:38.460 --> 15:39.320
met you,

15:39.360 --> 15:41.220
I thought you were really pretty.

15:41.270 --> 15:41.830
Later,

15:42.240 --> 15:42.820
as I

15:42.820 --> 15:44.310
slowly got to know you,

15:44.750 --> 15:46.010
I realized you're even more

15:46.010 --> 15:47.410
beautiful on the inside.

15:48.170 --> 15:49.400
I know I'm not

15:49.480 --> 15:50.360
that outstanding.

15:50.360 --> 15:52.010
But I really hope that

15:52.750 --> 15:54.240
if you have anything to say,

15:54.240 --> 15:55.120
or when you're upset,

15:55.120 --> 15:56.410
you can talk to me.

15:56.500 --> 15:58.430
And if you run into any trouble,

15:58.820 --> 15:59.670
I can help you.

16:00.130 --> 16:00.510
What I'm

16:00.510 --> 16:01.460
trying to say is

16:02.170 --> 16:03.970
I like you.
[T/N: muffled voice]

16:05.770 --> 16:07.050
I like you.
[T/N: muffled voice]

16:07.050 --> 16:07.480
Um...

16:07.500 --> 16:07.840
I...

16:08.110 --> 16:09.340
I have things to do tomorrow.

16:09.340 --> 16:10.140
I've got to go.

16:10.370 --> 16:10.840
Ranran.

16:11.770 --> 16:14.170
T-This coil of incense isn't finished yet.

16:15.440 --> 16:17.770
Put it out.
We can light it again next time.

16:18.240 --> 16:18.860
Wait.

16:19.440 --> 16:21.400
Let's walk and talk.

16:23.620 --> 16:27.750
[Seasons Change Hostel]

16:25.410 --> 16:26.270
Feuds can

16:27.100 --> 16:27.960
cause de...

16:28.580 --> 16:31.450
Cause the living to die,

16:32.000 --> 16:34.070
and the dead to live.

16:35.370 --> 16:36.860
When I no longer obz...

16:37.840 --> 16:38.900
When I no longer...

16:40.410 --> 16:41.090
Gosh.

16:41.340 --> 16:41.960
Whenever I recite lines,

16:41.960 --> 16:43.910
I mix up my nasal sounds.

16:44.510 --> 16:45.580
It's so annoying.

16:45.670 --> 16:46.530
Practice more.

16:50.790 --> 16:53.010
When I no longer obsess over love...

17:02.440 --> 17:04.680
Didn't you go to the film set?

17:04.960 --> 17:05.890
Why are you back?

17:08.000 --> 17:09.250
I'm just a nobody.

17:09.310 --> 17:10.910
The crew didn't give me a bed.

17:11.010 --> 17:13.020
The assistant director
told me to find some scenes

17:13.020 --> 17:15.329
portraying a range of emotions
for auditions.

17:15.329 --> 17:17.440
I've read through the script
a million times,

17:17.440 --> 17:19.069
but it still feels like
something is missing.

17:19.069 --> 17:19.640
What?

17:20.089 --> 17:21.640
You're nitpicking their script now?

17:21.640 --> 17:23.099
No, that's not what I mean.

17:23.200 --> 17:24.569
The... The entire script

17:24.569 --> 17:26.349
is great when read as a whole.

17:26.770 --> 17:27.920
But if you pick out single scenes,

17:27.920 --> 17:30.250
it somewhat feels disjointed.

17:30.500 --> 17:32.360
I don't know which part to choose.

17:32.500 --> 17:33.660
Aid the emotions...

17:33.660 --> 17:35.090
Oh, I get it now.

17:40.440 --> 17:41.980
Human emotions...

17:44.880 --> 17:46.010
And uniqueness.

17:47.380 --> 17:48.040
Xu Shengli.

17:48.660 --> 17:50.320
Look at this painting of mine.

17:52.250 --> 17:55.230
Your painting is quite avant-garde.

17:55.980 --> 17:57.170
What are you doing?

17:58.090 --> 17:58.500
Look.

17:58.500 --> 18:00.070
If the two people in my painting

18:00.070 --> 18:01.290
were both grinning

18:01.290 --> 18:02.160
and laughing,

18:02.550 --> 18:04.180
they'd look like 2 nutjobs.

18:04.740 --> 18:05.680
But if between the two of them,

18:05.680 --> 18:06.570
one is crying

18:06.570 --> 18:07.700
and the other is laughing,

18:07.700 --> 18:08.480
then when you look at it,

18:08.480 --> 18:10.210
there's room for imagination.

18:10.570 --> 18:11.370
But...

18:11.470 --> 18:13.570
Wait, just... keep it simple.

18:15.940 --> 18:17.050
There was a great painter
in the late Ming Dynasty

18:17.050 --> 18:17.810
named Zhu Da.

18:18.290 --> 18:19.820
His alias was Bada Shanren.

18:19.960 --> 18:21.330
Take his signature, for example.

18:21.330 --> 18:22.480
The writing on top

18:22.610 --> 18:24.080
looks like "cry",

18:24.330 --> 18:25.330
and the writing on the bottom

18:25.330 --> 18:26.520
looks like "laugh".

18:26.720 --> 18:28.400
So there is laughter in tears,

18:28.400 --> 18:29.660
and tears in laughter.

18:29.740 --> 18:31.110
My inspiration for painting

18:31.110 --> 18:31.900
comes from there.

18:31.900 --> 18:32.420
I get it.

18:33.640 --> 18:34.920
You mean

18:34.920 --> 18:36.610
joy, anger, sorrow, and happiness

18:36.610 --> 18:38.010
shouldn't be separated?

18:38.220 --> 18:39.280
Joy within sorrow,

18:39.660 --> 18:40.930
and sorrow within joy.

18:41.810 --> 18:42.660
That way,

18:43.790 --> 18:44.790
it has more depth.

18:45.960 --> 18:47.280
You catch on quick.

18:47.770 --> 18:50.610
Not bad, Master Cao.

18:56.530 --> 18:57.420
How's it going?

19:03.390 --> 19:04.320
That won't do.

19:05.090 --> 19:06.090
Here, let me do it.

19:08.430 --> 19:10.360
There's ghosting.

19:11.330 --> 19:12.930
You pulled it back and forth?

19:14.590 --> 19:15.290
Watch me.

19:17.710 --> 19:18.290
Go.

19:21.390 --> 19:21.910
See?

19:22.660 --> 19:23.300
You try.

19:25.030 --> 19:26.770
Zongbao, how do you know everything?

19:26.770 --> 19:27.960
I'm an actor.

19:27.990 --> 19:29.400
I have to know a bit of everything.

19:29.400 --> 19:30.880
I need to learn from you then.

19:30.880 --> 19:33.340
Screenwriters need to know everything too.

19:34.760 --> 19:36.800
It's tough working in this crew.

19:37.050 --> 19:39.180
I'm new here. Still have a lot to learn.

19:42.940 --> 19:44.070
How's the director?

19:44.810 --> 19:46.670
Did he read your script?

19:49.270 --> 19:50.510
To be honest,

19:50.550 --> 19:52.210
I've been in the crew for days,

19:52.380 --> 19:53.380
but I haven't even seen

19:53.380 --> 19:54.510
the back of his head.

19:55.640 --> 19:56.460
Film crews...

19:57.510 --> 19:59.380
are too busy—there's too much going on.

19:59.380 --> 20:00.680
Every time I go,

20:01.110 --> 20:02.160
I see those people,

20:02.160 --> 20:03.530
and they all seem very busy.

20:03.530 --> 20:05.410
If you really want to stay,

20:05.550 --> 20:07.610
you have to make people remember you.

20:10.070 --> 20:10.530
Come on.

20:12.200 --> 20:13.800
Call me if you need anything.

20:26.570 --> 20:27.360
Hello.

20:27.420 --> 20:29.210
The PA in your crew,

20:29.250 --> 20:30.000
named Xu Shengli.

20:30.000 --> 20:30.980
Where is he?

20:32.310 --> 20:32.970
Over there.

20:33.220 --> 20:34.050
Okay, thanks.

20:34.510 --> 20:35.170
No problem.

20:40.070 --> 20:41.400
Great Screenwriter Xu.

20:43.110 --> 20:43.820
Ranran?

20:44.200 --> 20:45.170
Why are you here?

20:45.250 --> 20:47.050
I'm doing a makeup test
for Director Ma's crew.

20:47.050 --> 20:48.700
They said Director Weng's
team is next door.

20:48.700 --> 20:50.030
I guessed you'd be here.

20:52.900 --> 20:54.360
Is this all you're eating?

20:54.740 --> 20:55.460
Well, I...

20:55.830 --> 20:58.160
I'm rushing to write something. It's due.

20:59.090 --> 21:00.550
If Zhuang Zhuang knew about this,

21:00.550 --> 21:01.860
she'd be heartbroken.

21:02.810 --> 21:04.250
Have a seat.

21:13.530 --> 21:16.030
Something's been off
between you two lately.

21:16.030 --> 21:16.640
Tell me.

21:17.900 --> 21:19.100
How did you upset her?

21:19.700 --> 21:22.230
What could possibly be off
between me and her?

21:24.420 --> 21:26.000
What's wrong with Zhuang Zhuang?

21:26.000 --> 21:26.610
Is that guy from Wenzhou

21:26.610 --> 21:27.370
bullying her again?

21:27.370 --> 21:28.900
I knew you would

21:28.900 --> 21:29.590
bring that up.

21:29.590 --> 21:30.270
Let me tell you,

21:30.270 --> 21:32.250
there is nothing going on between them.

21:32.250 --> 21:33.940
She's sick of him.

21:47.590 --> 21:48.670
Listen.

21:48.830 --> 21:50.590
You're not doing the clothing business

21:50.590 --> 21:51.510
anymore.

21:51.610 --> 21:53.180
Every day, apart from class,

21:53.180 --> 21:54.610
she locks herself in her room

21:54.610 --> 21:55.810
to practice singing.

21:56.980 --> 21:59.440
There must be some conflict
between you two.

21:59.960 --> 22:02.250
What conflict could we have?

22:03.720 --> 22:06.250
We just stopped
doing the clothing business.

22:07.570 --> 22:08.880
Who brought it up?

22:09.450 --> 22:10.830
She brought it up the other day.

22:10.830 --> 22:11.880
Impossible.

22:12.570 --> 22:14.200
That's definitely not what she meant.

22:14.200 --> 22:14.850
Tell me,

22:14.850 --> 22:16.310
what were her exact words?

22:19.290 --> 22:20.450
She said

22:21.790 --> 22:22.960
that at that time,

22:22.960 --> 22:24.990
we were both free

22:25.240 --> 22:26.240
and needed money,

22:27.210 --> 22:29.330
so we partnered up temporarily.

22:30.480 --> 22:33.140
We were bound to split up
sooner or later anyway.

22:33.200 --> 22:34.400
Is that it?

22:35.720 --> 22:37.610
You can't even read between the lines?

22:37.610 --> 22:39.740
And you call yourself a screenwriter.

22:39.960 --> 22:40.480
Well...

22:40.640 --> 22:42.700
Isn't that just the literal meaning?

22:44.500 --> 22:45.810
Anyway, listen.

22:45.920 --> 22:48.200
Zhuang Zhuang's concern for you

22:48.350 --> 22:49.750
has always been sincere.

23:17.590 --> 23:18.390
Kang Shunyin.

23:20.960 --> 23:22.220
Why are you here again?

23:23.790 --> 23:25.390
Zhuang Zhuang, you're back.

23:25.850 --> 23:26.620
You're back.

23:27.240 --> 23:27.970
Just in time.

23:28.290 --> 23:28.890
Come here.

23:28.960 --> 23:30.070
I... I bought you...

23:30.070 --> 23:31.160
lots of things you like...

23:31.160 --> 23:31.980
you like to eat.

23:31.980 --> 23:32.640
Look here.

23:32.740 --> 23:34.600
I don't want them. Take them away.

23:36.270 --> 23:37.500
You don't like them?

23:37.830 --> 23:38.720
Then let's go.

23:38.980 --> 23:40.680
I'll take you to a r-r...

23:40.760 --> 23:42.000
...restaurant.

23:42.020 --> 23:42.420
Let's go.

23:42.420 --> 23:43.050
Don't

23:43.050 --> 23:43.860
make a drunken scene here.

23:43.860 --> 23:44.790
I'm telling you.

23:44.960 --> 23:46.030
Are you done?

23:46.050 --> 23:47.460
Didn't you create
enough trouble last time?

23:47.460 --> 23:48.750
If you don't want me to make a scene,

23:48.750 --> 23:49.900
let me inside.

23:50.010 --> 23:51.290
I'll explain everything inside.

23:51.290 --> 23:52.070
Can't I?

23:52.220 --> 23:52.890
Zhuang Zhuang.

23:52.890 --> 23:53.780
Are you okay?

23:54.160 --> 23:54.690
I'm fine.

23:56.200 --> 23:58.410
How about we go to their room to chat?

23:58.550 --> 23:59.660
-Let's go.
-What are you doing?

23:59.660 --> 24:00.990
Are you out of your mind?

24:02.800 --> 24:04.460
I'm sorry. Go inside quickly.

24:09.200 --> 24:09.610
I'm...

24:10.480 --> 24:11.630
I'm sorry.

24:15.750 --> 24:16.610
Zhuang Zhuang.

24:16.610 --> 24:17.250
Let me tell you something.

24:17.250 --> 24:18.440
This apartment...

24:18.740 --> 24:21.260
You can't stay here anymore.

24:21.570 --> 24:23.350
You have to come back with me

24:23.790 --> 24:25.050
to Wenzhou.

24:26.440 --> 24:27.340
Get up.

24:27.680 --> 24:28.550
No, I won't.

24:28.680 --> 24:30.740
Get up. You're getting the bed dirty.

24:31.900 --> 24:33.430
Then I'll take off my pants.

24:33.500 --> 24:34.250
It won't be dirty anymore, right?

24:34.250 --> 24:34.680
Kang Shunyin.

24:34.680 --> 24:35.740
Are you kidding me?

24:35.880 --> 24:37.060
I'm serious.

24:37.420 --> 24:38.530
I'm serious.

24:38.590 --> 24:39.660
I'm pursuing my happiness.

24:39.660 --> 24:40.760
I'm serious.

24:41.850 --> 24:42.590
Zhuang Zhuang.

24:42.590 --> 24:44.190
Come back to Wenzhou with me.

24:45.240 --> 24:46.300
Come back to Wenzhou with me.

24:46.300 --> 24:47.900
Come back to Wenzhou with me!

24:50.060 --> 24:51.060
You won't, right?

24:51.480 --> 24:52.000
Fine.

24:52.470 --> 24:53.200
If you won't,

24:53.240 --> 24:54.260
I'll pack for you.

24:54.370 --> 24:55.700
Th-this is your stuff, right?

24:55.700 --> 24:56.500
What are you doing?

24:56.500 --> 24:58.000
That belongs to someone else.

24:58.000 --> 24:59.330
Then which ones are yours?

24:59.330 --> 25:00.240
These are yours?

25:00.240 --> 25:01.220
Alright. Come on.

25:01.220 --> 25:02.440
I... I'll pack for you.

25:02.440 --> 25:03.580
Okay? Come on.

25:03.650 --> 25:05.050
I'm packing your things.

25:05.700 --> 25:06.830
I'll open the bag for you.

25:06.830 --> 25:07.440
It's empty.

25:07.440 --> 25:08.750
I'll put everything inside for you.

25:08.750 --> 25:09.240
Come.

25:09.810 --> 25:10.580
Look at these.

25:10.580 --> 25:11.720
So many beautiful clothes.

25:11.720 --> 25:13.450
I'll take them all back for you.

25:13.960 --> 25:15.220
Such beautiful clothes...

25:15.220 --> 25:16.420
Let's wear them back in Wenzhou.

25:16.420 --> 25:17.220
So beautiful.

25:17.310 --> 25:18.250
And these,

25:18.460 --> 25:19.300
dresses.

25:19.480 --> 25:20.770
They aren't suitable

25:20.770 --> 25:22.790
for this gloomy city.

25:22.880 --> 25:23.290
And...

25:43.290 --> 25:46.220
You're actually wearing
matching outfits with him?

25:57.360 --> 25:59.020
I'm wearing the same clothes.

25:59.880 --> 26:01.310
I want us to wear matching outfits.

26:01.310 --> 26:01.730
I...

26:03.920 --> 26:05.290
Wearing matching couple's outfits
with him?

26:05.290 --> 26:06.660
Wearing matching couple's outfits
with him?

26:06.660 --> 26:08.200
What exactly do you want?

26:08.220 --> 26:09.070
Let's see how you're going to
wear the same clothes as him now!

26:09.070 --> 26:09.980
Shameless!

26:10.090 --> 26:11.440
If you really cared about your dignity...

26:11.440 --> 26:12.180
I'll tear this off you.

26:12.180 --> 26:13.200
I'll show you shame!

26:13.200 --> 26:14.740
Wearing matching couple's outfits
with him?

26:14.740 --> 26:16.190
Don't push your luck!

26:16.270 --> 26:17.180
I'm trying to be patient

26:17.180 --> 26:18.040
talking to you.

26:18.250 --> 26:20.610
Just like the Three Visits to the Hut,
I've come twice now!

26:20.610 --> 26:22.340
I'm giving you one last chance.

26:23.160 --> 26:24.270
I'm giving you one last chance.

26:24.270 --> 26:25.100
Okay?

26:25.460 --> 26:26.320
Zhuang Zhuang.

26:26.980 --> 26:28.240
Be with me.

26:28.810 --> 26:30.220
Can't you just be with me?

26:30.220 --> 26:31.070
Zhuang Zhuang.

26:31.070 --> 26:32.920
I'm begging you, okay?

26:33.530 --> 26:34.480
Northeasterner.

26:34.480 --> 26:35.880
That guy was drunk and making a scene.

26:35.880 --> 26:36.720
He wouldn't leave the door.

26:36.720 --> 26:38.030
He even wanted to come into my room.

26:38.030 --> 26:38.810
Northeasterner.

26:38.810 --> 26:40.010
You have to handle this.

26:40.010 --> 26:40.770
How am I supposed to handle it?

26:40.770 --> 26:41.590
Go get the keys.

26:41.590 --> 26:42.180
What's wrong? What are they arguing about?

26:42.180 --> 26:43.200
It's between the couple...

26:43.200 --> 26:44.110
Well, that man...

26:44.110 --> 26:45.290
T-T-That Gut Cook

26:45.290 --> 26:45.940
is here again!

26:45.940 --> 26:46.770
He's making a scene in the room.

26:46.770 --> 26:47.500
The Gut Cook?

26:47.550 --> 26:48.220
I'll go ask.

26:48.220 --> 26:49.310
Don't cause more trouble.

26:49.310 --> 26:50.590
They went into the room together.

26:50.590 --> 26:51.920
How can you handle this?

26:51.960 --> 26:53.740
Just watch for a while. We...

26:53.850 --> 26:54.940
What happened to Zhuang?

26:54.940 --> 26:55.640
Just... that...

26:55.640 --> 26:58.160
Zhuang Zhuang's fellow villager
from Wenzhou is here.

26:58.160 --> 26:59.460
Zhuang Zhuang, listen to me.

26:59.460 --> 27:00.810
Let go! Let go of me.

27:00.810 --> 27:02.810
-I’ll change. I’ll change.
-Let go!

27:02.850 --> 27:04.380
-I’ll change it. OK?
-Let go!

27:04.380 --> 27:04.790
Let go.

27:05.140 --> 27:06.890
Get the keys. Open the door.

27:07.480 --> 27:08.570
What are you standing there for?

27:08.570 --> 27:09.570
Go open it. Hurry.

27:10.750 --> 27:11.940
Zhuang Zhuang, open the door.

27:11.940 --> 27:12.550
Zhuang Zhuang!

27:12.550 --> 27:14.210
I was all alone in Wenzhou,

27:14.250 --> 27:15.900
while you were living it up in Beijing.

27:15.900 --> 27:17.010
I'm telling you,
I'm going to call the police!

27:17.010 --> 27:17.850
Call the police. Go ahead.

27:17.850 --> 27:18.380
When the police come,

27:18.380 --> 27:19.420
they'll say I'm the victim too.

27:19.420 --> 27:21.180
Move. Move out of the way.

27:21.420 --> 27:22.180
Open the door.

27:22.180 --> 27:23.640
Zhuang Zhuang, I like you.

27:24.740 --> 27:25.400
What are you doing?

27:25.400 --> 27:26.530
Are you being a pervert?

27:26.530 --> 27:27.590
What are you doing?

27:27.790 --> 27:28.500
Get out.

27:28.530 --> 27:29.590
What are you doing?

27:30.050 --> 27:31.000
What are you doing?

27:31.000 --> 27:32.030
You're being a pervert!

27:32.030 --> 27:33.090
What are you doing?

27:39.420 --> 27:40.530
-Take him away. Take him away.
-Let’s go.

27:40.530 --> 27:41.590
Go, hurry up and go.

27:43.050 --> 27:43.900
Let me tell you.

27:43.900 --> 27:45.400
I wasn't being a pervert. Zhuang Zhuang.

27:45.400 --> 27:46.960
Zhuang Zhuang, I'm your fiancé.

27:46.960 --> 27:48.460
Why are you grabbing me?

27:48.460 --> 27:49.860
Go to the police station.

27:50.000 --> 27:51.330
Where do you think you are,
acting like a pervert?

27:51.330 --> 27:53.260
-Get up.
-Go to the police station.

27:54.380 --> 27:55.500
You stand right there.

27:55.500 --> 27:56.450
Stand still!

27:59.010 --> 28:00.340
What are you looking at?

28:00.960 --> 28:01.980
Go away!

28:02.050 --> 28:03.510
Mind your own business!

28:03.790 --> 28:04.640
Move along!

28:48.590 --> 28:50.080
If I'd known,

28:50.810 --> 28:51.850
I would've sent him

28:51.850 --> 28:53.380
to Tang's.

28:53.510 --> 28:54.930
You were pinned down.

28:55.090 --> 28:55.770
So what?

28:55.770 --> 28:57.000
Why send him to Tang's?

28:57.000 --> 28:58.460
We should've castrated him.

28:58.460 --> 28:59.530
Even so, Xu Shengli

28:59.530 --> 29:00.510
has to do it himself.

29:00.510 --> 29:02.310
Zongbao, does castrate mean...

29:08.330 --> 29:10.060
You finally decided to show up?

29:10.500 --> 29:11.700
Where else would I go?

29:12.030 --> 29:13.560
It was total chaos in there!

29:13.720 --> 29:15.090
Where?

29:15.110 --> 29:16.660
The Gut Cook came again.

29:18.750 --> 29:19.810
He bullied Zhuang Zhuang?

29:19.810 --> 29:20.810
That's putting it mildly.

29:20.810 --> 29:23.140
That's serious enough to land him in jail!

29:23.380 --> 29:24.200
Wait, wait!

29:24.330 --> 29:25.640
I drove him away.

29:25.640 --> 29:26.900
Zhuang Zhuang is fine.

29:27.610 --> 29:28.350
Well, if you can't speak properly,

29:28.350 --> 29:29.580
just talk less.

29:29.960 --> 29:30.810
What do you mean

29:30.810 --> 29:31.750
"enough to land him in jail"?

29:31.750 --> 29:33.680
You want to blow this up, don't you?

29:34.140 --> 29:36.160
I'm just reporting to him.

29:37.350 --> 29:38.810
There were so many people.

29:39.900 --> 29:40.480
Even...

29:41.460 --> 29:42.030
Even if

29:42.810 --> 29:43.980
she wasn't scared,

29:45.030 --> 29:45.850
as...

29:46.850 --> 29:47.510
as a girl...

29:48.830 --> 29:49.380
right?

29:51.480 --> 29:53.140
If you put it that way, indeed,

29:53.140 --> 29:53.800
at the time,

29:53.830 --> 29:56.290
there were many people there.

29:56.420 --> 29:58.700
Zhuang Zhuang probably

29:58.700 --> 29:59.740
feels bad.

30:12.400 --> 30:14.700
Go see her if you want.

31:12.220 --> 31:13.000
Mr. Xu.

33:53.770 --> 33:55.300
Where did you go this early?

33:55.310 --> 33:56.640
I went to get breakfast.

34:02.960 --> 34:05.010
I also checked

34:05.290 --> 34:07.350
if there were any strangers outside.

34:08.110 --> 34:08.739
And?

34:09.070 --> 34:09.889
It turned out,

34:10.230 --> 34:11.360
outside in the yard,

34:11.940 --> 34:13.050
there was only one

34:13.090 --> 34:14.920
beauty carrying breakfast.

34:17.090 --> 34:17.480
Here.

34:18.020 --> 34:19.219
I bought this for you.

34:19.840 --> 34:20.360
Try it.

34:23.860 --> 34:25.590
It's my favorite jellied tofu.

34:26.150 --> 34:27.030
It's sweet.

34:28.420 --> 34:28.880
Come on.

34:34.960 --> 34:35.630
Eat.

34:41.880 --> 34:42.810
It's delicious.

34:48.860 --> 34:49.320
Zhuang.

34:50.440 --> 34:52.310
Are you taking 3 classes

34:52.330 --> 34:53.780
every week now?

34:56.320 --> 34:57.600
Mr. Zheng said the troupe

34:57.600 --> 34:59.300
has an opening for an understudy,

34:59.300 --> 35:00.710
so I need to practice hard.

35:00.710 --> 35:02.110
You can definitely do it.

35:07.550 --> 35:08.150
By the way,

35:08.330 --> 35:09.980
for the lock on our door,

35:10.190 --> 35:11.250
here is the new key.

35:11.320 --> 35:12.150
Keep it safe.

35:29.610 --> 35:30.670
This place is good.

35:31.010 --> 35:32.540
I'll buy it again next time.

35:34.940 --> 35:36.050
When you are on set,

35:36.070 --> 35:36.980
is the daily work

35:36.980 --> 35:37.880
very tiring?

35:41.110 --> 35:42.260
It's alright.

35:42.260 --> 35:43.760
When we start filming,

35:43.760 --> 35:45.360
time passes pretty quickly.

35:45.780 --> 35:46.860
But this bit of tiredness

35:46.860 --> 35:47.730
is nothing.

35:52.130 --> 35:53.280
You're not actually worried

35:53.280 --> 35:54.280
about me, are you?

35:54.960 --> 35:55.420
No way.

35:57.300 --> 35:58.560
I am worried about you.

36:02.650 --> 36:03.710
Eat up.

36:04.210 --> 36:05.340
I'll clean up after.

37:10.510 --> 37:11.880
Okay. Good.

37:12.300 --> 37:12.940
Great.

37:15.420 --> 37:16.150
Take a break.

37:21.150 --> 37:23.440
About the money lost last time,

37:23.510 --> 37:24.620
how is that going?

37:25.760 --> 37:26.760
We're still selling

37:26.760 --> 37:27.980
the leftover clothes.

37:27.980 --> 37:29.510
We should have some money
by the end of the month.

37:29.510 --> 37:31.170
I'll pay you as soon as I get it.

37:32.460 --> 37:34.660
I have to wait until the end of the month?

37:36.500 --> 37:37.510
Mr. Zheng, I...

37:39.550 --> 37:40.070
Okay.

37:40.690 --> 37:41.550
Let's see

37:41.550 --> 37:42.730
Page 12.

37:42.780 --> 37:44.090
Page 12.

37:48.130 --> 37:48.990
Zhuang Zhuang.

37:53.280 --> 37:55.860
I had more classes
this month than last month.

37:56.800 --> 37:58.410
Take this to tide you over.

37:59.190 --> 37:59.590
Here.

37:59.590 --> 38:00.750
This isn't appropriate, Mr. Zheng.

38:00.750 --> 38:02.320
What's inappropriate?

38:02.510 --> 38:04.190
Just consider it doing me a favor.

38:04.190 --> 38:05.450
Take it to my wife.

38:06.840 --> 38:07.570
I can't.

38:08.360 --> 38:09.490
Don't say no.

38:09.590 --> 38:10.690
If you don't,

38:10.760 --> 38:13.100
I'm really done for.

38:16.260 --> 38:17.070
Hurry, hurry.

38:23.010 --> 38:23.670
Zhuang Zhuang,

38:23.670 --> 38:24.800
did you earn all this

38:25.070 --> 38:26.640
from selling clothes?

38:26.860 --> 38:27.990
That was fast.

38:29.090 --> 38:29.940
I wish I had a daughter

38:29.940 --> 38:31.170
like you.

38:31.900 --> 38:33.030
I made steamed buns today.

38:33.030 --> 38:34.560
Come try some after class.

38:35.510 --> 38:37.460
Mrs. Zheng, actually...

38:37.530 --> 38:38.390
Zhuang Zhuang.

38:39.300 --> 38:40.500
Break is over.

38:40.610 --> 38:41.560
Time for class.

38:41.880 --> 38:43.210
I know. Stop rushing us.

38:43.210 --> 38:44.740
Can't we just chat for a bit?

38:46.510 --> 38:48.010
Zhuang Zhuang, hurry up and go to class.

38:48.010 --> 38:49.410
Mr. Zheng is rushing you.

38:49.500 --> 38:50.090
Hurry up.

38:51.820 --> 38:52.530
Good luck.

39:36.550 --> 39:39.170
I went for a makeup test a while ago.

39:39.500 --> 39:41.760
I ran into Mr. Xu in the neighboring crew.

39:41.920 --> 39:43.950
He was eating alone in a corner.

39:43.980 --> 39:45.310
He looked so miserable.

39:56.940 --> 39:57.570
Zongbao.

39:58.230 --> 39:59.110
What's wrong with you?

39:58.470 --> 39:59.730
[Registration Room]

40:01.000 --> 40:03.090
Acting is hard on the back.

40:03.120 --> 40:04.490
For veteran actors,

40:04.550 --> 40:06.590
eight out of ten

40:06.730 --> 40:08.120
have bad backs.

40:08.590 --> 40:10.250
Didn't you go to the hospital?

40:10.630 --> 40:11.740
Why waste that money?

40:11.740 --> 40:12.820
It'll heal with some rest.

40:12.820 --> 40:14.130
[Registration Room]

40:13.210 --> 40:14.010
Wait a second.

40:14.340 --> 40:14.760
What?

40:16.530 --> 40:17.660
Come inside with me.

40:18.110 --> 40:19.070
What do you want?

40:19.260 --> 40:19.990
To fix you up.

40:20.500 --> 40:20.880
What?

40:26.710 --> 40:27.370
Feels good.

40:32.000 --> 40:33.050
Keep it down.

40:33.260 --> 40:35.090
People will think I did something to you.

40:35.090 --> 40:35.480
What?

40:36.940 --> 40:38.200
Out of a white dye vat,

40:38.300 --> 40:40.330
can you get black cloth?

40:41.000 --> 40:43.380
Right here. Right here.

40:44.360 --> 40:44.900
Done.

40:47.550 --> 40:48.700
Get up. Move around.

40:49.010 --> 40:49.940
See how it feels.

40:54.510 --> 40:55.580
You know what?

40:56.230 --> 40:57.450
I do feel

40:57.600 --> 40:58.690
much lighter.

41:00.360 --> 41:01.120
Zongbao.

41:02.070 --> 41:03.640
The roles you play every day

41:03.690 --> 41:05.420
are quite varied, aren't they?

41:06.230 --> 41:08.130
Well, being an actor is about

41:08.390 --> 41:11.620
playing all kinds of characters.

41:13.480 --> 41:15.890
So, do laborers earn more,

41:16.190 --> 41:17.590
or do handymen earn more?

41:21.070 --> 41:21.870
I'm not picky.

41:22.490 --> 41:23.620
I'll play anything.

41:24.280 --> 41:25.880
Just trying to make a living.

41:32.890 --> 41:36.000
You're still not done with your work?

41:38.420 --> 41:39.280
Go to sleep.

41:40.280 --> 41:42.790
Health is your greatest asset.

41:48.030 --> 41:49.060
This girl

41:49.630 --> 41:50.490
is really dumb.

41:52.730 --> 41:54.500
That's where you don't get it.

41:55.420 --> 41:56.790
She may seem a bit

41:56.900 --> 41:58.370
dumb in this scene,

41:58.800 --> 41:59.860
but actually,

41:59.900 --> 42:01.880
the director wants to use this scene

42:01.880 --> 42:03.010
to see if the actress

42:03.150 --> 42:04.050
can perceive that

42:04.050 --> 42:05.710
she's actually playing dumb.

42:05.980 --> 42:07.360
If you act like she's really stupid,

42:07.360 --> 42:08.290
then it's wrong.

42:08.460 --> 42:09.790
There's a lot more to it.

42:14.940 --> 42:15.940
Crap. Crap. Crap.

42:45.210 --> 42:46.010
Who is this...

42:46.530 --> 42:48.190
kind person?
